<div class="container section" id="about">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>About</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="section-body">
    Wild Card is a Boston-based mixed Ultimate Frisbee team that was formed in 2012. In our two years of existence, Wild Card has grown into a team characterized by youthful energy, never-say-die attitudes, and good sportsmanship. 
    <br>
    <br>
    In our first year, we qualified for Club Nationals by finishing 4th in the New England region -- a notable accomplishment for our inaugural season. We finished the season ranked 15th in the country. In our second season, we again qualified for Club Nationals. Entering the tournament ranked 10th, we made an impressive run to the semifinals. Ultimately finishing 4th in the country, we earned both a spot in USA Ultimate's Pro Flight and an invitation to the World Ultimate Club Championships.
    <br>
    <br>
    We are unbelievably excited to have the honor of representing the United States at the World Ultimate Club Championships in Lecco, Italy this August!
